\lambda_{+}\left(E\right):=\int_{E}f_{+}d\mu
\quad\lambda_{-}\left(E\right):=\int_{E}f_{-}d\mu
\lambda\left(E\right):=\lambda_{+}\left(E\right)-\lambda_{-}\left(E\right)
